may use GPS technology (or other similar technology) to determine your current location in order to determine the city you are located within and display a location map with relevant advertisements. <span style="color: #333333; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.759260177612305px; text-align: start;">YourKart</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.759260177612305px; text-align: start;"> </span>will not share your current location with other <span style="color: #333333; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.759260177612305px; text-align: start;">YourKart</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.759260177612305px; text-align: start;"> </span>users or partners. If you do not want <span style="color: #333333; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.759260177612305px; text-align: start;">YourKart</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.759260177612305px; text-align: start;"> </span>to use your location for the purposes set forth above, you should turn off the location services for the <span style="color: #333333; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.759260177612305px; text-align: start;">YourKart</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.759260177612305px; text-align: start;"> </span>application located in your <span style="color: #333333; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.759260177612305px; text-align: start;">YourKart</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.759260177612305px; text-align: start;"> </span>account settings or in your mobile phone settings. <strong style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 18px !important;">By using this Website or the Service, you consent to collection, storage, and use of the personal information you provide for any of the Services that we offer, and you consent to our collection of any changes or updates that you may provide to any information you provide that is collected by </strong><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.759260177612305px; text-align: start;"><strong>YourKart</strong></span><strong style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 18px !important;">.</strong></p>
<p style="border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; line-height: 18px; width: 650px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12px ! important; line-height: 18px ! important; text-decoration: underline;">B. Cookies</span></p>
