<p style="border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; line-height: 18px; width: 650px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12px ! important; line-height: 18px ! important; text-decoration: underline;">F. Accessing and Modifying Personal Information and Communication Preferences</span></p>
